        "## Question 8:Implement a simple attention-based encoder-decoder model for English-to-Spanish translation using Tensorflow or PyTorch.\n",
        "(Include your Python code and output in the code box below.)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "PqwDfEB9zbn3"
      }
