        "## Question 10: Imagine you are building a creative writing assistant for a publishing company. The assistant should generate story plots and character descriptions using Generative AI. Describe how you would design the system, including model selection, training data, bias mitigation, and evaluation methods. Explain the real-world challenges you might face.\n",
        "(Include your Python code and output in the code box below.)\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "### 1. SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Core Components:\n",
        "\n",
        "**A. Input Layer:**\n",
        "- User prompts (genre, themes, setting, tone)\n",
        "- Existing content database\n",
        "- Author preferences and style guidelines\n",
        "\n",
        "**B. AI Model Layer:**\n",
        "- **Plot Generation Model**: Fine-tuned GPT-4 or similar LLM\n",
        "- **Character Generation Model**: Specialized model for character attributes\n",
        "- **Style Transfer Module**: Adapts output to specific writing styles\n",
        "- **Coherence Checker**: Validates logical consistency\n",
        "\n",
        "**C. Processing Pipeline:**\n",
        "1. Prompt Engineering & Input Parsing\n",
        "2. Context Retrieval (RAG - Retrieval Augmented Generation)\n",
        "3. Generation with constraints\n",
        "4. Post-processing & refinement\n",
        "5. Human review interface\n",
        "\n",
        "**D. Output Layer:**\n",
        "- Structured plot outlines\n",
        "- Character profiles with backstories\n",
        "- Scene descriptions\n",
        "- Dialogue suggestions\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "### 2. MODEL SELECTION\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Primary Model: GPT-4 / Claude / Llama 3\n",
        "**Rationale:**\n",
        "- Strong creative writing capabilities\n",
        "- Context length: 8k-100k tokens\n",
        "- Few-shot learning for specific genres\n",
        "- Fine-tunable for domain adaptation\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Alternative/Complementary Models:\n",
        "- **Cohere Command**: For structured outputs\n",
        "- **Anthropic Claude**: For safety and nuance\n",
        "- **Custom Fine-tuned models**: Genre-specific (mystery, romance, sci-fi)\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Model Configuration:\n",
        "```python\n",
        "model_config = {\n",
        "    'temperature': 0.8,  # Balance creativity & coherence\n",
        "    'top_p': 0.9,\n",
        "    'max_tokens': 2000,\n",
        "    'presence_penalty': 0.6,  # Encourage diversity\n",
        "    'frequency_penalty': 0.3\n",
        "}\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
