        "- Licensed story databases\n",
        "- Publisher's own catalog (with rights)\n",
        "- Creative Commons licensed fiction\n",
        "\n",
        "**Curated Datasets:**\n",
        "- Plot summaries from IMDb, Wikipedia\n",
        "- Character databases (TV Tropes, Fandom wikis)\n",
        "- Writing prompt databases\n",
        "- Genre-specific corpora\n",
        "\n",
        "**Data Volume:**\n",
        "- 10,000+ complete novels\n",
        "- 50,000+ short stories\n",
        "- 100,000+ character descriptions\n",
        "- 500,000+ plot summaries\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Data Preprocessing:\n",
        "1. **Cleaning**: Remove metadata, formatting artifacts\n",
        "2. **Structuring**: Tag genres, themes, character types\n",
        "3. **Deduplication**: Identify and remove duplicates\n",
        "4. **Quality Filtering**: Remove low-quality or problematic content\n",
        "5. **Augmentation**: Paraphrase and vary existing content\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Fine-tuning Strategy:\n",
        "```\n",
        "Base Model (GPT-4)\n",
        "    ↓\n",
        "Domain Adaptation (General Fiction)\n",
        "    ↓\n",
        "Genre-Specific Fine-tuning\n",
        "    ↓\n",
        "Human Feedback (RLHF)\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "### 4. BIAS MITIGATION\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Identified Bias Risks:\n",
        "\n",
        "**A. Representation Bias:**\n",
        "- Gender stereotypes in character roles\n",
        "- Racial/ethnic underrepresentation\n",
        "- Cultural bias towards Western narratives\n",
        "- LGBTQ+ representation gaps\n",
        "\n",
        "**B. Content Bias:**\n",
        "- Genre stereotypes and clichés\n",
        "- Harmful tropes (e.g., \"bury your gays\")\n",
        "- Socioeconomic biases\n",
        "- Age and disability representation\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Mitigation Strategies:\n",
        "\n",
        "**1. Data Diversification:**\n",
        "- Include works from diverse authors (50%+ non-male, 40%+ non-white)\n",
        "- International literature representation\n",
        "- Contemporary and historical works\n",
        "- Indie and traditional publications\n",
        "\n",
        "**2. Bias Detection Systems:**\n",
        "```python\n",
        "bias_checks = [\n",
        "    'gender_balance_analyzer',\n",
