        "    'stereotype_detector',\n",
        "    'harmful_trope_identifier',\n",
        "    'cultural_sensitivity_scorer'\n",
        "]\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "**3. Constrained Generation:**\n",
        "- Explicit diversity requirements in prompts\n",
        "- Anti-bias prompts: \"Avoid stereotypes\"\n",
        "- Character diversity templates\n",
        "- Multi-cultural name databases\n",
        "\n",
        "**4. Human-in-the-Loop:**\n",
        "- Diversity readers for output review\n",
