        "\n",
        "### 6. REAL-WORLD CHALLENGES\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Technical Challenges:\n",
        "\n",
        "**1. Coherence Over Long Narratives:**\n",
        "- **Problem**: Models lose track of plot threads\n",
        "- **Solution**:\n",
        "  - Hierarchical generation (outline → chapters → scenes)\n",
        "  - External memory systems\n",
        "  - Consistency checkers\n",
        "\n",
        "**2. Character Consistency:**\n",
        "- **Problem**: Character traits change unexpectedly\n",
        "- **Solution**:\n",
        "  - Character profile databases\n",
        "  - Trait tracking systems\n",
        "  - Periodic consistency checks\n",
        "\n",
        "**3. Creative Stagnation:**\n",
        "- **Problem**: Repetitive plots and tropes\n",
        "- **Solution**:\n",
        "  - High temperature sampling\n",
        "  - Prompt engineering for novelty\n",
        "  - Ensemble methods\n",
        "\n",
        "**4. Computational Cost:**\n",
        "- **Problem**: Large models are expensive\n",
        "- **Solution**:\n",
        "  - Model distillation\n",
        "  - Efficient architectures\n",
        "  - Caching common generations\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Business Challenges:\n",
        "\n",
        "**1. Author Acceptance:**\n",
        "- **Problem**: Writers may resist AI assistance\n",
        "- **Solution**:\n",
        "  - Position as collaborative tool\n",
        "  - Emphasize augmentation, not replacement\n",
        "  - Provide creative control\n",
        "\n",
        "**2. Quality Control:**\n",
        "- **Problem**: Variable output quality\n",
        "- **Solution**:\n",
        "  - Multi-stage review process\n",
        "  - Quality thresholds\n",
        "  - Human editorial oversight\n",
        "\n",
        "**3. Intellectual Property:**\n",
        "- **Problem**: Who owns AI-generated content?\n",
        "- **Solution**:\n",
        "  - Clear usage agreements\n",
        "  - Hybrid human-AI authorship models\n",
        "  - Legal consultation\n",
        "\n",
        "**4. Market Differentiation:**\n",
        "- **Problem**: All publishers using similar AI\n",
        "- **Solution**:\n",
        "  - Custom fine-tuning\n",
        "  - Unique style development\n",
        "  - House-specific training\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Ethical Challenges:\n",
        "\n",
        "**1. Plagiarism Risk:**\n",
        "- **Problem**: AI may memorize training data\n",
        "- **Solution**:\n",
        "  - Plagiarism detection systems\n",
        "  - Novelty verification\n",
        "  - Attribution tracking\n",
        "\n",
        "**2. Job Displacement:**\n",
        "- **Problem**: Impact on human writers\n",
